{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_vrtx_01PTtfjGb6bi8ZLzQfD3irQZ","type":"tool_result","content":"File created successfully at: /Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizmkit/specs/043-web-font-size-accessibility-toggle/plan.md"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5162696b-eb1f-43c4-9e42-4383048021a9","uuid":"a6ffd893-cb4c-4acd-a51f-813b96adf8af","timestamp":"2026-03-23T08:26:08.335Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"create","filePath":"/Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizmkit/specs/043-web-font-size-accessibility-toggle/plan.md","content":"# Plan — F-043: Web Font Size Accessibility Toggle\n\n## Key Components\n\n- **CSS**: Add `--font-scale` CSS var to `:root`, apply `font-size: calc(1rem * var(--font-scale))` to `body`, three size values: small=0.875, medium=1.0, large=1.2\n- **HTML**: Add font-size toggle control (button group) to header area, three buttons: 小/中/大, with active state styling\n- **JS**: Font size loading/saving to localStorage (separate key `prizmclaw-font-size`), apply scale to `document.documentElement`, wire button click handlers\n\n## Data Flow\n\n1. `init()` → `loadFontSize()` → reads localStorage → calls `applyFontSize(scale)` → sets CSS var on `<html>`\n2. User clicks toggle button → `setFontSize(scale)` → saves to localStorage → `applyFontSize(scale)` → updates active button\n3. On page reload → step 1 restores persisted scale\n\n## Files to Modify\n\n- `public/styles.css`: add `--font-scale: 1` to `:root`, `font-size: calc(1rem * var(--font-scale))` to `body`, `.font-toggle` button group styles\n- `public/index.html`: add `<div class=\"font-toggle\">` to header with 3 buttons\n- `public/js/main.js`: add font toggle constants, `els.fontToggleBtns`, `applyFontSize()`, `loadFontSize()`, `setFontSize()`, wire click handlers in `init()`\n\n## Tasks\n\n- [ ] T1: Add `--font-scale: 1` to `:root` in styles.css; add `font-size: calc(1rem * var(--font-scale))` to `body`; add `.font-toggle` button group CSS\n- [ ] T2: Add font toggle HTML (三个按钮 小/中/大) to `<header class=\"app-header\">` in index.html\n- [ ] T3: Add JS constants `FONT_SIZE_KEY`, scales map; add `els.fontToggleBtns`; implement `applyFontSize()`, `loadFontSize()`, `setFontSize()`; wire handlers; call `loadFontSize()` in `init()`\n","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null}}
